{"tid":2054919,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[達爾文獎2020出爐] 無裝備爬富士山直播跌死 日本主播得奬 !  [有片]","createTime":"2020-06-07T13:58:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-07T14:29:15.000Z","uid":1267,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"93cd2ad48351a2ec97fe6e4b1b8d1517299103ea","tid":2054919,"uid":1267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T13:58:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/fitz.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/達爾文獎2020-日本主播得_1.jpg?w=1209&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Ffitz.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F06%2F%E9%81%94%E7%88%BE%E6%96%87%E7%8D%8E2020-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E4%B8%BB%E6%92%AD%E5%BE%97_1.jpg%3Fw%3D1209%26ssl%3D1&h=ffde385c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「達爾文獎」Darwin Awards 相信係諾貝爾獎之外，另一個受人注目嘅科學「大獎」。「達爾文獎」係紀念因為愚蠢方式而喪命，違反達爾文進化論嘅人。今年出爐嘅「達爾文獎」得主，包括呢位日本網台主播 Tedzu。<br />\n<br />\n2019年10月28日早上，網上平台 niconico 以「富士山GO」為題進行直播，拍攝主播 Tedzu 著住行街嘅休閒服，行上富士山實況。喺接近滿佈白雪嘅山頂位置時，Tedzu 不斷叫住「好滑」、\b「手好凍」等，然後鏡頭由山上跌落，觀眾打電話報警。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=13&amp;v=CoUJ7mLGFzA&amp;feature=emb_logo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D13%26v%3DCoUJ7mLGFzA%26feature%3Demb_logo&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUrXxB%2B4AiQz8bo105MOPl14%3D&h=7c8ee249\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=13&amp;v=CoUJ7mLGFzA&amp;feature=emb_logo</a><br />\n<br />\n到10月30日下午，救援人員喺七合目，大概喺大陽館以南約800米 (大約海拔3000米) 發現一具屍體，經認屍後證明為主播 Tedzu。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/fitz.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/達爾文獎2020-日本主播得_6.jpg?w=967&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Ffitz.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F06%2F%E9%81%94%E7%88%BE%E6%96%87%E7%8D%8E2020-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E4%B8%BB%E6%92%AD%E5%BE%97_6.jpg%3Fw%3D967%26ssl%3D1&h=e348e911&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTedzu 就係爬過左邊呢個欄杆，然後跌落懸崖<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/fitz.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/達爾文獎2020-日本主播得_8.jpg?w=1289&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Ffitz.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F06%2F%E9%81%94%E7%88%BE%E6%96%87%E7%8D%8E2020-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E4%B8%BB%E6%92%AD%E5%BE%97_8.jpg%3Fw%3D1289%26ssl%3D1&h=407bec08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n悲劇英雄 Vs 愚蠢玩家<br />\n<br />\n雖然達爾文獎官方以 Pinnacle Of Stupidity (愚蠢的山峰) 去形容主播 Tedzu 嘅行為，不過根據日本媒體事後嘅查證，Tedzu 並非愚不可及。<br />\n<br />\nTedzu 喪生時47歲，大學主修法律，不過一直不能通過專業考試，做唔到律師。於是，Tedzu 漸漸失去生活動力，走去網台做主播。佢嘅節目以日常生活為主，都係拍攝佢周圍踩單車或跑步情況，節目做咗幾年，觀眾唔多。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/fitz.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/達爾文獎2020-日本主播得_002.jpg?w=1213&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Ffitz.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F06%2F%E9%81%94%E7%88%BE%E6%96%87%E7%8D%8E2020-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E4%B8%BB%E6%92%AD%E5%BE%97_002.jpg%3Fw%3D1213%26ssl%3D1&h=438ba1e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTedzu 生前在東京獨居，住喺一間偏僻嘅小單位。鄰居話佢甚少朋友，唔太覺佢有返工，覺得佢係隱閉中年。<br />\n日本有媒體問 Tedzu嘅 拍檔，話發生意外當日，有網民留言話想睇下富士山嘅雪，唔知係咪因為咁令 Tedzu 上富士山。不過 Tedzu 近年好鍾意行富士山，有時甚至拎啲飲品上山派畀遊客。<br />\n媒體亦發現 Tedzu 死前已患上末期癌症，生存率只有1%。佢喺直播節目中亦有提及，並且有搵過東京好多間醫院求診。"},{"pid":"485656492c9754fa7826cfab3388938bfea79f29","tid":2054919,"uid":1267,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T13:58:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://fitz.hk/sports/hiking/達爾文獎2020-無裝備爬富士山直播跌死-日本主播得奬/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffitz.hk%2Fsports%2Fhiking%2F%E9%81%94%E7%88%BE%E6%96%87%E7%8D%8E2020-%E7%84%A1%E8%A3%9D%E5%82%99%E7%88%AC%E5%AF%8C%E5%A3%AB%E5%B1%B1%E7%9B%B4%E6%92%AD%E8%B7%8C%E6%AD%BB-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E4%B8%BB%E6%92%AD%E5%BE%97%E5%A5%AC%2F&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUrXxB%2B4AiQz8bo105MOPl14%3D&h=81e9d7cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fitz.hk/sports/hiking/達爾文獎2020-無裝備爬富士山直播跌死-日本主播得奬/</a>"},{"pid":"a42f2b504eb30058cdac3b319842662da0d5c04e","tid":2054919,"uid":112581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T14:00:27.000Z","msg":"算唔算死都要煩到人<img src=\"/assets/fa